The Raven's run could make someone scared, because when a decent weight armor is rushing at you, and at a decent speed, like a train or a tank speeding up to its fullest, you can involuntarily think that death is imminent. For the girl, the lull was fleeting and the twisting of the chain could probably keep her company. But the Raven burst in only a couple of moments later through the door, almost carrying her out, well, after that the door was locked. Raymon once again recreated his copies, and each of them slowly surrounded Bella, the rotation of the scythe multiplied, as if his copies were able to clone themselves, but this was not the case. The original was among this "crowd", having prepared the second hand for a counter attack, or repelling any opponent's blow.
